trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs class is used to supply event values to the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event and to enable you to specify a custom Windows identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs används för att ange händelsevärden för den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>händelse och så att du kan ange en anpassad Windows-identitet för den aktuella begäranden.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Du kan komma åt den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>händelsen för den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>klass genom att ange en subrutin med namnet **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** i filen Global.asax för ASP.NET-program.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> constructs a AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs object using the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>konstruerar ett AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs-objekt med aktuellt <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>och skickar det till den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property of the AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs object supplied to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>egenskapen för AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs angivet objekt till den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse att ange anonym identifierare för ett anpassat värde.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte anger ett värde för den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>egenskapen under den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse en <xref:System.Guid>används.</xref:System.Guid> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when the anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelsen aktiveras endast när anonym identifiering är <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> constructs a <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object using the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>Skapar ett <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs>objekt med hjälp av aktuellt <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule>

trans-unit.source: It then passes the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: Därefter skickas den <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs>objekt till den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The context for the event.
trans-unit.target: Kontexten för händelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the anonymous identifier for the user.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den anonyma identifieraren för användaren.

trans-unit.source: You can use the AnonymousID property to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda egenskapen AnonymousID för att ange anonym identifierare för ett anpassat värde under den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse.

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the AnonymousID property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte anger ett värde för egenskapen AnonymousID under den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelse en <xref:System.Guid>används.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when the anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** händelsen aktiveras endast när anonym identifiering är <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: The anonymous identifier for the user.
trans-unit.target: Den anonyma identifieraren för användaren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> objekt för den aktuella HTTP-begäranden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> provides access to <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> objects for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>ger åtkomst till <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, och <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>objekt för den aktuella begäranden.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> objekt för den aktuella HTTP-begäranden.
